narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great class. A lot of interesting readings and close analyses.
A great introductory expository writing course.
Take it!! English 114 really helped my writing abilities. The workload varies depending on which professor you choose, but the clas is a great experience either way.

Absolutely. Although this class was particularly useful to me because I had no background in academic writing, I noticed that even students who had the appropriate backgrounds took a lot from this class.
